{"tid":648135,"cid":18,"subCid":0,"title":"一帶一路交流區","createTime":"2018-04-30T12:00:45.000Z","updateTime":"2018-05-04T09:59:06.000Z","uid":177244,"like":1,"dislike":15,"uniUserReply":5,"replies":[{"pid":"6a9d9ba8a564b5a56db672dba28e979168455aec","tid":648135,"uid":177244,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-04-30T12:00:45.000Z","msg":"香港應該點發揮制度、法治、國際聯繫、專業服務等優勢，拓展一帶一路市場？一帶一路點為香港帶來新定位、新機遇？歡迎交流各行各業資訊。"},{"pid":"6761837b2a209647e3a83e7816fa7dbd93f098c7","tid":648135,"uid":51701,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-04-30T12:01:59.000Z","msg":"Hide Blocked User - 物產豐隆"},{"pid":"af92dbdce15ead83e6dc74b0281b913b5f0151c2","tid":648135,"uid":177244,"like":0,"dislike":2,"score":-2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-04-30T12:04:24.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://www.hk01.com/tag/702\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.hk01.com%2Ftag%2F702&d=8wzt19psbD7LDmiXDxLXk7ZGMQxn7aheim1dKZ3ASAU%3D&h=d38bec65\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.hk01.com/tag/702</a><br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"http://www.master-insight.com/tag/%E4%B8%80%E5%B8%B6%E4%B8%80%E8%B7%AF/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fwww.master-insight.com%2Ftag%2F%25E4%25B8%2580%25E5%25B8%25B6%25E4%25B8%2580%25E8%25B7%25AF%2F&d=8wzt19psbD7LDmiXDxLXk7ZGMQxn7aheim1dKZ3ASAU%3D&h=77bcaffe\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">http://www.master-insight.com/tag/%E4%B8%80%E5%B8%B6%E4%B8%80%E8%B7%AF/</a><br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://asean.thenewslens.com/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fasean.thenewslens.com%2F&d=8wzt19psbD7LDmiXDxLXk7ZGMQxn7aheim1dKZ3ASAU%3D&h=40874a35\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://asean.thenewslens.com/</a>"},{"pid":"1a0d24107edd55f5fec6ca6be44bc0b13aade5cd","tid":648135,"uid":156068,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-04-30T12:10:15.000Z","msg":"有無人真係去個d地方讀書?"},{"pid":"4e18ff9ec82344d69c11fab695022fbada993601","tid":648135,"uid":177244,"like":0,"dislike":2,"score":-2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-04-30T12:14:31.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://www.youtube.com/playlist?list=PLymA3lZecWBXACt3Mmnx8qV1Uq8mnyMOn\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.youtube.com%2Fplaylist%3Flist%3DPLymA3lZecWBXACt3Mmnx8qV1Uq8mnyMOn&d=8wzt19psbD7LDmiXDxLXk7ZGMQxn7aheim1dKZ3ASAU%3D&h=8177fe56\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.youtube.com/playlist?list=PLymA3lZecWBXACt3Mmnx8qV1Uq8mnyMOn</a><br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.youtube.com/playlist?list=PL0eGJygpmOH7mTq8TqFG28nByLRvMNXvt\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.youtube.com%2Fplaylist%3Flist%3DPL0eGJygpmOH7mTq8TqFG28nByLRvMNXvt&d=8wzt19psbD7LDmiXDxLXk7ZGMQxn7aheim1dKZ3ASAU%3D&h=7da0e187\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.youtube.com/playlist?list=PL0eGJygpmOH7mTq8TqFG28nByLRvMNXvt</a>"},{"pid":"7fa4670ddc93fe813fb057acf22788ee6d13ef57","tid":648135,"uid":47359,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-04-30T14:35:45.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/04/30/223538_ea3dc39ca0b2f6b5f17abddec1f0e9a4.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F04%2F30%2F223538_ea3dc39ca0b2f6b5f17abddec1f0e9a4.png&h=f1f25ab6&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"06700204d6ae46544cea25f67f3cef29742cfb86","tid":648135,"uid":177244,"like":0,"dislike":2,"score":-2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-05-01T12:24:55.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"ee19b6c37b05a74eca155af28f05b468e564a7c6","tid":648135,"uid":48083,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-05-01T12:28:46.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/05/01/202831_7c7ac91e5a6fd3fcb1631a7816f21cb2.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F05%2F01%2F202831_7c7ac91e5a6fd3fcb1631a7816f21cb2.png&h=36d9e724&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/05/01/202840_98f66acb27d53577b7d3bb4c365d50a3.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F05%2F01%2F202840_98f66acb27d53577b7d3bb4c365d50a3.png&h=17581ccf&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/05/01/202845_a5cf310551d8c228b08b20f04ca20ba7.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F05%2F01%2F202845_a5cf310551d8c228b08b20f04ca20ba7.png&h=92622df8&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"69fac4fee216009262706262da84c59ab332a94a","tid":648135,"uid":177244,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-05-01T17:06:19.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"758af7a820d66d1bd2796a6432f58b9ef0d98e82","tid":648135,"uid":177244,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-05-04T03:48:26.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"2797d1bc6c97828ac7a5071770aa66fa5459f901","tid":648135,"uid":177244,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-05-04T09:43:04.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"http://www.beltandroad.gov.hk/important-speeches_20180203_tc.html\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fwww.beltandroad.gov.hk%2Fimportant-speeches_20180203_tc.html&d=8wzt19psbD7LDmiXDxLXk7ZGMQxn7aheim1dKZ3ASAU%3D&h=897df384\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">http://www.beltandroad.gov.hk/important-speeches_20180203_tc.html</a><br />\n<br />\n政策溝通不斷深入，國際影響與日俱增。共建&ldquo;一帶一路&rdquo;倡議得到國際社會越來越多的關注和回應，並被納入聯合國大會等國際組織的相關決議。我國已同86個國家和國際組織簽署了101份共建&ldquo;一帶一路&rdquo;合作文件，同30多個國家開展機制化的產能合作，朋友圈越來越大。2017年5月，首屆&ldquo;一帶一路&rdquo;國際合作高峰論壇在北京成功舉行，29位外國國家元首和政府首腦齊聚北京，140多個國家和80多個國際組織的高級別代表出席會議。習近平主席在高峰論壇上發表的重要講話引發強烈共鳴，會議達成270多項合作成果，凝聚起推進&ldquo;一帶一路&rdquo;建設的廣泛共識。<br />\n<br />\n設施聯通不斷加強，陸海天網立體發展。蒙內鐵路、亞吉鐵路正式通車，雅萬高鐵、中老鐵路、中俄和中亞油氣管道、吉布提港等一批重要項目穩步推進。中歐班列累計開行近7000列，國內開行城市達到38個，通達歐洲13個國家35個城市。一個以中巴、中蒙俄、新亞歐大陸橋等經濟走廊為引領，以陸海空通道和信息高速路為骨架，以鐵路、港口、管網等重大工程為依託的複合型基礎設施網路正在形成。<br />\n<br />\n貿易暢通不斷提升，合作紐帶日益鞏固。區域全面經濟夥伴關係協定談判取得積極進展，&ldquo;一帶一路&rdquo;自貿區網路加快構建。中國對有關國家的直接投資存量超過1000億美元。中國企業在有關24個國家建設75個境外經貿合作區，入駐企業3800多家。2014年至2016年，中國同&ldquo;一帶一路&rdquo;有關國家貿易總額超過3萬億美元，2017年貿易額達1.1萬億美元，增長迅速。<br />\n<br />\n資金融通不斷擴展，多元投融資支撐體系加快建設。已有10家中資銀行在26個國家設立67家一級機構，金融機構海外佈局進展迅速。我國已與24個國家中央銀行簽訂了約1.4萬億元人民幣的雙邊本幣互換協定，人民幣國際化進程穩步推進。國家開發銀行、中國進出口銀行、各商業銀行以及絲路基金支持&ldquo;一帶一路&rdquo;建設的力度不斷加大。<br />\n<br />\n民心相通不斷深化，人文交流豐富多彩。我國與有關國家累計簽署了40餘項科技合作協議和300多個文化交流執行計畫，設立了138所孔子學院、135個孔子課堂、16個中醫藥海外中心，建立了45個國際聯合實驗室和研究中心。我國還與有關國家廣泛開展衛生、旅遊、減貧、綠色環保、防止沙漠化等領域合作，力所能及提供對外援助。這些人文交流合作增進了我國同各國人民之間的了解和友誼。"},{"pid":"7159397a325b2500d02b4ce6e12faf4f32e74e73","tid":648135,"uid":177244,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-05-04T09:43:57.000Z","msg":"發揮&ldquo;香港所長&rdquo;，合力提升優勢互補效應。我國是當今世界第二大經濟體，人口眾多，市場巨大，發展勢頭強勁。我國還是第一製造業大國，在全球500餘種主要工業產品中有220多種產量位居第一，高鐵、核電、通信設備等高端裝備製造技術已達到國際一流甚至領先水準。香港背靠祖國，面向世界，是重要的國際金融、航運、貿易中心，是全球公認的最自由、最開放的經濟體，國際經貿聯繫廣泛，服務業非常發達。香港服務業門類全、人才多、專業化和國際化程度高，特別是金融、會計、法律、設計、諮詢等專業服務享譽全球，加之&ldquo;兩文三語&rdquo;通用、知識產權保護完備、市場和法制與國際接軌等有利因素，具有很強的國際競爭力。香港的專業服務與內地製造業優勢互補，&ldquo;拼船出海&rdquo;，必將產生1加1大於2的協同效應。"},{"pid":"bae6f72d8bfdc2ca2b60ae49981f9e0f6a67c13f","tid":648135,"uid":177244,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-05-04T09:48:22.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://www.news.gov.hk/chi/2018/04/20180417/20180417_214159_706.html\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.news.gov.hk%2Fchi%2F2018%2F04%2F20180417%2F20180417_214159_706.html&d=8wzt19psbD7LDmiXDxLXk7ZGMQxn7aheim1dKZ3ASAU%3D&h=d5890532\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.news.gov.hk/chi/2018/04/20180417/20180417_214159_706.html</a><br />\n<br />\n特區政府正按去年12月簽署的《國家發展和改革委員會與香港特別行政區政府關於支持香港全面參與和助力「一帶一路」建設的安排》，成立聯席會議機制，協調落實安排內的措施，初步計劃於今年上半年召開首次會議，就「一帶一路」建設中的重大問題和合作事項與國家發展和改革委員會進行溝通協商。<br />\n<br />\n自從2月於北京舉辦論壇後，商務及經濟發展局局長邱騰華上月率領商界，包括四大商會，和由會計、金融、法律和解決爭議服務，及初創企業等界別的企業家和專業人士組成的代表團，訪問柬埔寨和越南，本月底我亦會率領代表團訪問另一個東盟國家印尼，為香港企業探索在「一帶一路」沿線的項目和機遇。此外，我們正與泰國政府緊密聯繫，希望盡快在泰國設立新的經貿辦事處。<br />\n<br />\n政府正與貿易發展局合作，加強和提升其「一帶一路」網站的功能，以期讓它作為提供最新和最全面有關「一帶一路」資料的一站式平台；貿發局也同時會研究提供線上和線下商業配對服務，為業界提供最新的「一帶一路」資訊，協助企業尋找合適的「一帶一路」項目。「發展品牌、升級轉型及拓展內銷市場的專項基金」（BUD基金）除了會獲得額外注資15億元外，資助範圍也由內地擴大至東盟，進一步協助香港企業拓展市場。"},{"pid":"896a37e643704c4dd4d8073acf9b1e5218ee840d","tid":648135,"uid":177244,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-05-04T09:50:16.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"http://m.hktdc.com/business-news/article/%E4%B8%80%E5%B8%B6%E4%B8%80%E8%B7%AF/%E4%B8%80%E5%B8%B6%E4%B8%80%E8%B7%AF-%E6%A9%9F%E9%81%87%E8%88%87%E9%A2%A8%E9%9A%AA/obor/tc/1/1X000000/1X0ADPFI.htm\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fm.hktdc.com%2Fbusiness-news%2Farticle%2F%25E4%25B8%2580%25E5%25B8%25B6%25E4%25B8%2580%25E8%25B7%25AF%2F%25E4%25B8%2580%25E5%25B8%25B6%25E4%25B8%2580%25E8%25B7%25AF-%25E6%25A9%259F%25E9%2581%2587%25E8%2588%2587%25E9%25A2%25A8%25E9%259A%25AA%2Fobor%2Ftc%2F1%2F1X000000%2F1X0ADPFI.htm&d=8wzt19psbD7LDmiXDxLXk7ZGMQxn7aheim1dKZ3ASAU%3D&h=cd9011fb\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">http://m.hktdc.com/business-news/article/%E4%B8%80%E5%B8%B6%E4%B8%80%E8%B7%AF/%E4%B8%80%E5%B8%B6%E4%B8%80%E8%B7%AF-%E6%A9%9F%E9%81%87%E8%88%87%E9%A2%A8%E9%9A%AA/obor/tc/1/1X000000/1X0ADPFI.htm</a><br />\n<br />\n&quot;一帶一路&quot;是2013年由習近平主席提出的&quot;二十一世紀海上絲綢之路&quot;和&quot;絲綢之路經濟帶&quot;共同構建的重大倡議。<br />\nBRI和OBOR均表示&quot;一帶一路&quot;倡議。<br />\n&quot;一帶一路&quot;的五大目標：加強政策溝通、設施聯通、貿易暢通、資金融通、民心相通。<br />\n現有的雙邊和多邊合作機制將用於加速促進沿途各國經濟一體化並支持貿易增長。<br />\n&quot;一帶一路&quot;對所有國家和組織開放。然而，官方地圖和文件強調了亞洲、中東、東非和東歐60多個國家的重要性。<br />\n大多數投資迄今集中在基礎設施、能源和採礦，從肯尼亞的標準軌距鐵路項目、柬埔寨水電項目到巴基斯坦的褐煤儲量開發項目。<br />\n海上絲綢之&quot;路&quot;對消費者和工業企業將是一個巨大的機會。不包括中國，這條路涵蓋了全球42%的人口和25%的GDP。<br />\n內陸&quot;帶&quot;連接世界最大經濟體中的兩個：中國和歐洲。這條路線將成為一個主要的物流通道，提供能源和礦業領域的重大機會。<br />\n我們估計中國&quot;一帶一路&quot;有關項目在未來五年的價值將約為3,500億美元。"},{"pid":"9d4a7511011bce55e17d35a41492326aa2d49d8a","tid":648135,"uid":177244,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-05-04T09:56:37.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"http://www.beltandroadsummit.hk/tc/index.html\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fwww.beltandroadsummit.hk%2Ftc%2Findex.html&d=8wzt19psbD7LDmiXDxLXk7ZGMQxn7aheim1dKZ3ASAU%3D&h=1c89d428\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">http://www.beltandroadsummit.hk/tc/index.html</a><br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"http://www.beltandroad.gov.hk/index_tc.html\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fwww.beltandroad.gov.hk%2Findex_tc.html&d=8wzt19psbD7LDmiXDxLXk7ZGMQxn7aheim1dKZ3ASAU%3D&h=8e3394db\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">http://www.beltandroad.gov.hk/index_tc.html</a><br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://beltandroad.hktdc.com/tc/belt-and-road-basics\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fbeltandroad.hktdc.com%2Ftc%2Fbelt-and-road-basics&d=8wzt19psbD7LDmiXDxLXk7ZGMQxn7aheim1dKZ3ASAU%3D&h=df8a5c3b\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://beltandroad.hktdc.com/tc/belt-and-road-basics</a><br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.brgcc.hk/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.brgcc.hk%2F&d=8wzt19psbD7LDmiXDxLXk7ZGMQxn7aheim1dKZ3ASAU%3D&h=393501b7\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.brgcc.hk/</a><br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://m21.hk/friendship/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fm21.hk%2Ffriendship%2F&d=8wzt19psbD7LDmiXDxLXk7ZGMQxn7aheim1dKZ3ASAU%3D&h=e2675bed\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://m21.hk/friendship/</a>"},{"pid":"49b890f39d562d611bbed6f63705993ef0068164","tid":648135,"uid":177244,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-05-04T09:56:54.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/05/04/175651_a20ea3c7059ea74d286b002c1ff36bf9.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F05%2F04%2F175651_a20ea3c7059ea74d286b002c1ff36bf9.png&h=ed111a79&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"e768df6740c3d322cb62089fc0d9a15dacfa0105","tid":648135,"uid":177244,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-05-04T09:57:40.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"http://www.capital-hk.com/article-keywords/689/yi-dai-yi-lu\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fwww.capital-hk.com%2Farticle-keywords%2F689%2Fyi-dai-yi-lu&d=8wzt19psbD7LDmiXDxLXk7ZGMQxn7aheim1dKZ3ASAU%3D&h=ddfa6495\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">http://www.capital-hk.com/article-keywords/689/yi-dai-yi-lu</a>"},{"pid":"eee1618015edbd888ccf2973cebc5a68d2797812","tid":648135,"uid":177244,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-05-04T09:59:06.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://news.now.com/home/opinion/detail?catCode=125&amp;topicId=676\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.now.com%2Fhome%2Fopinion%2Fdetail%3FcatCode%3D125%26topicId%3D676&d=8wzt19psbD7LDmiXDxLXk7ZGMQxn7aheim1dKZ3ASAU%3D&h=622b7034\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.now.com%2Fhome%2Fopinion%2Fdetail%3FcatCode%3D125%26topicId%3D676&h=2264d18f\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://news.now.com/home/opinion/detail?catCode=125&amp;topicId=676</a>"}]}